n Optimismus und Pessimismus in allen drei Theorien, wodurch deutlich wird, wie sich pessimistische Momente in den Gesamtzusammenhang dieser Weltbeschreibungen fügen.  afunded by Carl und Charlotte Schott-Stiftung an der Philipps-Universität Marburg  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Nov 2021) 0aCarl Schmitt. 0aCriticism of Culture. 0aGiorgio Agamben. 0aKulturkritik. 0aMichel Foucault. 0aPessimism. 0aPhilosophie. 0aPhilosophy. 0aPolitical sciencexPhilosophy. 0aPolitical science. 0aPolitics. 0aPolitik. 0aPolitikwissenschaft. 0aPolitische Philosophie. 0aPolitische Theorie. 4aCarl Schmitt. 4aGiorgio Agamben. 4aKulturkritik. 4aMichel Foucault. 4aPhilosophie. 4aPolitik. 4aPolitikwissenschaft. 4aPolitische Philosophie. 4aPolitische Theorie. 7aPHILOSOPHY / Political.2bisacsh  aCarl Schmitt.  aCriticism of Culture.  aGiorgio Agamben.  aMichel Foucault.  aPhilosophy.  aPolitical Philosophy.  aPolitical Science.  aPolitical Theory.  aPolitics.2 aCarl und Charlotte Schott-Stiftung an der Philipps-Universität Marburgefunder.4fnd4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/fnd08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus eBook-Package 2017z978311071954308iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2018z9783110603255oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Philosophy 2018z9783110603217oZDB-23-DPH40uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9783839441510zCo-access DOI >> click Walter de Gruyter40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783839441510423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783839441510/original  a978-3-11-071954-3  DG Plus eBook-Package 2017b2017  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_PLTLJSIS  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DGGb2